---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  lang="en"
  title="Delete Your Data | Open Compass"
  description="How to request deletion of your data from Open Compass apps."
>
  <main class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-primary-blue mb-6">Delete Your Data</h1>
    <p class="text-slate-700 mb-8">
      If you want to be deleted from our apps, please send a data deletion request to
      <a href="mailto:contact@opencompass.org" class="text-primary-blue underline">contact@opencompass.org</a>.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-blue mb-3">Short Procedure</h2>
    <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-slate-700">
      <li>Send an email to contact@opencompass.org from your registered email address.</li>
      <li>Use the subject: <strong>Data Deletion Request</strong>.</li>
      <li>Include the app name and any account details that help us identify your account.</li>
      <li>We will confirm receipt and process your request as required by applicable law.</li>
    </ol>
  </main>
</Layout>
